<a class="title" href="/nodes/96425/comments/1409354">Re: Code supprimé</a>
</h2>
<p class="meta">
Posté par <a href="/users/zenitram" rel="author">Zenitram</a> (<a href="http://mediaarea.net">page perso</a>) <time class="updated" datetime="2012-11-16T15:52:55+01:00"><span class="date">le 16/11/12</span> <span class="time">à 15:52</span></time>.
