<a class="title" href="/nodes/96425/comments/1408802">Re: Code supprimé</a>
</h2>
<p class="meta">
Posté par <a href="/users/elessar" rel="author">ﻥ Tanguy Ortolo</a> (<a href="http://tanguy.ortolo.eu/">page perso</a>) <time class="updated" datetime="2012-11-15T14:19:17+01:00"><span class="date">le 15/11/12</span> <span class="time">à 14:19</span></time>.
